  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC285">
        <l>muṟṟiya vummait tokaiccoṉ maruṅki</l>
        <l>ṉeccak kiḷavi yurittu mākum.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/172/mode/1up">172</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/173/mode/1up">173</ref>.</p>
      
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC285-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘pattum koṭāṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉṟakkāl,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC285-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>ellāmkoṭāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉṟumām.
      </p>
      <p>
‘tokaiccol’ eṉṟataṉāṉ, ellāṅkoṇṭām, koṇṭār eṉṟum; ellārum vārār eṉṟum, varuvar eṉṟum koḷḷappaṭum.
      </p>
      <p>
eccavummai oḻivupporuḷai uṭaittāṉatupōla, muṟṟummaiyum oḻivup poruḷpaṭa varum eṉṟu koḷka. (37)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n223/mode/1up">220</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. muṟṟummaiyaṭuttu niṉṟa tokaiccolliṭattu eccaccollurittumām. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u - m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC285-Cena-cit1">
        <l>pattuṅkoṭāl,</l>
      </lg>
     <lg xml:id="TolC285-Cena-cit2">
        <l>aṉaittuṅkoṭāl</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpuḻi muṟṟummai tamporuḷuṇarttātu cilaveñcakkoṭuveṉṉum poruḷ tōṉṟi niṉṟavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka.
      </p>
      <p>
muṟṟutaleṉṉum poruḷatu paṇpu muṟṟiyavummaiyeṉa oṟṟumai nayattāṟ coṉmēlēṟi niṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
urittumākumeṉavē, eccapporuṇmai kuṟiyātu niṟṟalē perumpāṉmaiyeṉpatām.
      </p>
      <p>
ēṟpuḻikkōṭaleṉpataṉāṉ eccappaṭuvatu etirmaṟaiviṉaikkaṇeṉṟu koḷka. pattuṅkoṭu eṉpatu piṟavuṅ koṭu veṉpatu paṭa niṟṟaliṉ, vitiviṉaikkaṇṇum eccaṅ kuṟikkumeṉpārumuḷar. ippoḻutu pattuṅkoṭu eṉpatu karuttāyiṉ, ippoḻutu pattukkoṭu eṉa ummaiyiṉṟiyum poruḷ peṟappaṭum; pattuṅkoṭu piṟavuṅkoṭu eṉpatu karuttāyiṉ, iḵteccavummaiyākaliṉ īṇṭaikkeytātu; ataṉāṉ atu poruttamiṉṟeṉka.
      </p>
      <p>
ivai mūṉṟu cūttirattāṉum vaḻuvaṟkaveṉa iṭaiccoṟpaṟṟi marapuvaḻukkāttavāṟu.	(37)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/310/mode/1up">310</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/311/mode/1up">311</ref>.</p>
      <p>
muṟṟummai yeccavummaiyākum vaḻuvamaiti muṟṟiya vummait tokaic coṉmaruṅkiṉeccak kiḷavi yurittu mākum.
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>muṟṟiya vummait tokaic coṉmarunki</l>
        <l>ṉeccak kiḷavi yurittu mākum.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
itu, muṟṟummai yecca vummaiyām poruṭkumeṉa vaḻuvamaikkiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
  (i-ḷ) muṟṟiya vummait tokaic coṉ maruṅkiṉ ― muṟṟummai yaṭuttu niṉṟa peyarum viṉaiyuñ cārnta colliṭattu, eccakkiḷavi yurittumākum ― eccac collurittumāku meṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
eṉavē, eccapporuḷ kuṟiyātu niṟṟalē perumpāṉmai. ēṟpuḻik kōṭalāliḵtetir maṟaikkaṇṇateṉak koḷka.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC285-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>pattum koṭāl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC285-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>aṉaittum koṭāl.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṉum muṟṟummaikaḷ, cila ‘kiṭakkak koṭu’ eṉa veccap poruḷuṇartti niṉṟavāṟu kāṇka. tokaic coleṉṟataṉāṉē ‘ellārum vārā’ reṉap poruṭ peyarkkaṇṇuṅ koḷka. pattuṅ koṭu piṟavuṅ koṭu eṉpatu karuttāyiṉ aḵtecca vummaiyām. <num xml:lang="en">(37)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n189/mode/1up">182</ref>.</p>
      <p>
iḵtu ummaikkaṇ varuvatōr vēṟupāṭu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
i-ḷ: ― muṟṟummait tokaiccoṟ poruṇmaikkaṇ eccap poruṇmaiyum urittu. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
īṇṭut tokai eṉṟatu eṇṇiṉ tokai.
      </p>
      <p>
        u-m:―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC285-Tey-cit1">
        <l>niṉkaiyiṟ kāṇam pattuṅ koṭāl -</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻic cila koṭukka eṉṟavāṟām. itu maṟutta vāypāṭṭāṉallatu vārātu.	[36]
      </p>
    </body>
